 the party and brings one more mob back as the current one dies.  He backs his pet off upon reaching the group and tells it to attack the new mob.  It works quite well in the few zones I've partied with him in (Sebilis, PoV, other similar zones).  The main problem is if the mobs enrage upon low health and kills his pet every few pulls.  Oh and you will have to learn the max distance you can go while doing this.  If you go beyond a set range from your party, nobody gets experience when the mob dies.  This method makes for a constant stream of incoming mobs and is very good experience if things go right.<br>
